Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Miyako, let me introduce. This is Yuuzen. She's a very cooperative helper this time. Thanks to Yuuzen, Yoshino and friends were able to come to Hinayashiki.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Yuuzen. Doll master and sorcerer. I came with Yoshino and the others to help them, I have a personal interest in this Hinayashiki.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Miyako. I'm a sorceress of the M. Nishiki Railway Army...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: You know, the one I told you about, she's the one who made Nene run away.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Of course! I knew it!

Name: Miyako
Phrase: No, it's that... Yoshino told me about you and I thought you were a nice person.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: A good person?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Yoshino, what did ya tell this girl?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Nothing much, Yoshino just told her the whole truth.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yuuzen-san, how did you managed to get here? There must have been a trap set at that Gate. There were also curses that could not be easily broken. So how did you get to Hinayashiki?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I beat all those things. After recreating the Gate on my own, I located it and connected it with this Gate.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: How is that possible? Not only did you break goshujin-sama's spells, it's also impossible to create a unique route that goshujin-sama's can't intervene in...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: But, on the other hand, there are people who can do it.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Mah, they are older and have different experiences.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: But this Hinayashiki is a nice place. I haven't been in such a cosy place for a long time. The dolls who live here are all nice. If it weren't for the Mist, this would be the best house ever.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes, I think so too.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: It's the perfect house for doll otakus.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I thought I would meet some nice dolls here. I thought perhaps there's even living dolls.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Hey Miyako, yer sister is a doll too, isn't she? She can speak and walk on her own two feet. In addition, can she also use magic?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes, she can. Miyabi sometimes called herself a living doll. As you say, Miyabi can act of her own will. She can also use sorcery. It was also Miyabi who lifted my curse.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: On the summit of the Senbon Torii, a child wearing a fox mask told me, 'A living doll is waiting for you', I thought it must be Miyabi. I thought that if I came here, I would be able to meet Miyabi...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: But ya haven't met her yet?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: They are capricious ones. Once they leave yer side, they don't show themselves easily.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: But you'll see them sooner or later. Dolls love people.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: What is it? Staring at me? Do I smell like a doll?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: No, you don't stink at all! It's a very nice scent...

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Oooh-? Miyako is a bit cuter than usual.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I see that you are a well-known doll master. Your skill in sorcery is also quite good. Are you, by any chance, an acquaintance of Yae-san?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Even you say the same thing as Versailles. I'm from Iris Cloud. I have nothing to do with this Yae person.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I beg your pardon. I just thought you sounded like someone I know, so I...".

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I have a lot to talk about with ya. But ya know I can't talk about that in this situation. I just want to get the job done and get back to where I came from. Please do help me.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: But I have things to do...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I know. I'm going to defeat your master and return this mansion to a decent state. That's as far as I go.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Thank you very much. It's very reassuring to have someone like you on my side. I couldn't manage on my own at all.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: But Conductor and everyone are gone, right? Did you lose them on the way?

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: We were the only two people who got sent away before we could enter the mansion. Yoshino's doll was glowing, so maybe she did it?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: But we managed to get to Miyako without any trouble. Maybe that doll was on our side.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: The question is, how are we going to meet up with Shasho and the others?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Oh, don't worry about that. I have my shikigami with me.

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Shikigami?

Name: Putra
Phrase: Vivienne, over here next! Yuuzen's shikigami is dancing like a squid!

Name: Vivienne
Phrase: That's the strongest reaction I've ever seen. Putra then, we'll go with 'Breaching Putra' as planned!

Name: Putra
Phrase: I'll do it on the count of three!

Name: Putra
Phrase: Three, two, one...

Name: Putra
Phrase: HO! SMAAAAAAAAAASH!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: The door opens sideways.

Name: Putra
Phrase: Gaaaaarhahahahhhh! Sudden sliding door!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: Well, that's better.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: Miss Yoshino! And Miss Miyako too! You're safe!

Name: Yoshino
Phrase: We're all safe. Don't forget about Yuuzen, too.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Miyako! Are you alright!?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Versailles!

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Gosh, why does Miyako always have to do this?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I didn't mess up. I thought I could do it, but I couldn't.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Hmph, that's just like the Miyako I know.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I didn't expect Versailles to come. It's a strange feeling. I didn't expect Versailles to be inside Hinayashiki.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: I've always wanted to visit. It's the house where Miyako grew up.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I'd love to show you around, but it doesn't seem to be the Hinayashiki I know any more. I couldn't find Miyabi or goshujin-sama at all...

Name: Versailles
Phrase: It's been a few days since Miyako came here, yeah? During that time, have you been wandering around the house?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes. Nobody answered my calls. And when I tried to see her in person, the mansion became like a labyrinth. I couldn't get to goshujin-sama's room at all.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I don't really understand she's keeping Miyako away from her. If she wants ya for herself, why didn't she just take away yer freedom?

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: Don't say such scary words. What if that really happens?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: 'No, Yuuzen-san is right. I was wondering if goshujin-sama would do that.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: You thought that, and you came here all by yourself, Miyako? What is it with you? Do you like being scared?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Sorry. I don't have anything to be scared of...
Previously split apart, we were able to reach Miyako as we followed the shikigami released by Yuuzen's quick-thinking.
According to Miyako's story, Hinayashiki is ruled by her master's sorcery, and no matter how far she went, she will always come back to the same room.
Now, how to attack from here...

Name: Putra
Phrase: Aduhduhduh... Yoshino, if you're going to open it, tell me you're going to open it. I just dove headlong into a pile of dolls.

Name: Yakutsk
Phrase: GWAAAAAAAAAAAAAAH! PUTRA! WHAT THE HELL IS ON YOUR SHOULDER!?

Name: Putra
Phrase: What? My shoulder?

Name: Putra
Phrase: GYAAAAAHA! THERE'S A LONG-HAIRED NISHIKESE DOLL ON MY SHOULDER!
A long-haired doll was sitting, well behaved, on the shoulder of Putra, who had just plunged into a pile of dolls after a failed raid. Putra unintentionally threw the doll...

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: KORA! Don't throw the doll!
...Yuuzen brilliantly caught it. Using Putra as a springboard.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: If you do it like that, ya'll scare the doll. This girl had something to say and she sat on Putra's shoulders.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Isn't that right? The doll with beautiful hair.
-Okaeri.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: What's that? Can ya say it again?
--Okaeri. Okaeri.\n--Miyako, okaeri.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: I see. Ya're a friend of Miyako's, aren't cha? Ya're glad Miyako is back.
--Miyako, it's good to see you again! Let's play together again!\n--We missed you so much because Miyabi and Miyako were gone.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Oh my, what a clever girl you are. How do you know what's 'happy' and 'lonely'?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Miyako, shouldn't ya say something too?

Name: Miyako
Phrase: You, you can talk now.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: You haven't changed at all. Tiny, pretty, beautiful hair.
--Miyako, you can comb it again.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: Yes, of course. Come here.
The Nishikese doll, which spoke, went from Yuuzen's hands to Miyako's. But before Miyako touched the doll, she said a few words.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: I'm back. Thank you for waiting for me.
Miyako then takes the doll in her arms. However, Miyako did not run a comb through the doll's hair.
The Nishiki doll was waiting for Miyako's return. The moment she was placed in Miyako's arms, she crumbled and turned to ashes.

Name: Queensway
Phrase: The doll turned to ashes...

Name: Putra
Phrase: Oh no... Don't tell me, is it my fault?

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: No, no. It was destined to happen anyway.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: The doll was half transformed into a monster. She spoke with the last of her strength.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: She was a child who couldn't speak. She was turned into a demon because of goshujin-sama's sorcery, but she must have used magic to cast some kind of art on herself.'

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: She wanted to talk to Miyako. She knew this was her last chance, so she risked her life.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: She worked so hard up to this point. She believed that Miyako would come back to her.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: Don't worry. I will rescue yer friends.
Yuuzen spoke softly to the doll ashes and casted a sorcery.
Then, from the ashes, the sash of the kimono the doll was wearing floated up into the air. The doll then circled around Miyako before coming to a halt in the middle of the room.
--The next moment, the sliding door, which had been closed, opened.

Name: Versailles
Phrase: Miyako's friend opened the way for us.

Name: Yuuzen
Phrase: The dolls in this house are on our side too. Yoshino, Miyako. Don't miss the slightest hint. Sorcery can be dispelled with sorcery. If ya're part of the sorcerer's circle, ya too can break the spells of the monsters.

Name: Miyako
Phrase: ...Yes. Yuuzen-san.
Beyond the sliding doors, where the ashes of the doll indicated, darkness prevails. Even so, Miyako stepped out into the darkness without fear or hesitation.
